<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>As a participant in the Advanced Placement Program of the College Entrance Examination Board, Alvernia University awards college credit to high school students who do advanced work in high school and score well on Advanced Placement Examinations. In genera, credit is given for APE recommended scores.</i>
